So if we move to the right
one, we move up seven.

00:03:31.580 --> 00:03:34.540
Or if we move back one,
will move down seven.

00:03:34.540 --> 00:03:36.380
So we'll move down
seven, so the line

00:03:36.380 --> 00:03:37.680
